h1. Webmachine Loves Roar

_...and Roar Loves Webmachine!_


h2. Introduction

This is a sample application to show how [webmachine](https://github.com/seancribbs/webmachine-ruby) and [roar](https://github.com/apotonick/roar) can work together to build real RESTful systems in Ruby.


h2. Usage

To run the server:

  $ ruby server.rb

And, surprisingly, to run the client:

  $ ruby client.rb


